All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
App
Command-line entry point for the WhatsApp Chat Parser application.
AudioMessage
Represents a voice note or audio file attachment parsed from a WhatsApp chat export.
DocumentMessage
Represents a generic file attachment message parsed from a WhatsApp chat export.
ImageMessage
Represents a photo or image attachment parsed from a WhatsApp chat export.
Message
Abstract base class for all message types in the WhatsApp chat parser system.
Message.MessageType
Enumeration of all content categories supported by the WhatsApp chat parser.
StickerMessage
Represents an animated WebP sticker message parsed from a WhatsApp chat export.
TextMessage
Represents a plain-text message parsed from a WhatsApp chat export.
VideoMessage
Represents a video clip attachment parsed from a WhatsApp chat export.
WhatsAppChatParser
Stateless parser for WhatsApp chat export ZIP files.
WhatsAppChatParser.MediaEntry
Represents a media file entry in the ZIP archive.
WhatsAppExport
Immutable container for a fully-parsed WhatsApp chat export.
